name: Landmannalaugar
description:
This photo was taken in Iceland / Landmannalaugar by Teriell. It was published on unsplash.com on December 6, 2019.

Story of the photo:
The published photo was a huge success and is used in many places on the internet. Until today (2021/09/06) the published photo had 36.952.723 views via unsplash.
So this is clearly a traffic/reach highlight for any work of Teriell, who then got into the list of the 500 most seen contributors (only because of this image). 
This NFT represents the original file from unsplash, here is the reference: https://unsplash.com/photos/hmtD7tLRnws 

Any collector would own the ONLY NFT connected to a photo which was seen veeeeeery often :)
